snippet.title: The Sims 3 Supernatural Launch Video
snippet.description: The Sims 3 Supernatural is now available! Get a fresh look at the world of Moonlight falls and the adventures that await you there! How will you play with the supernatural? Cast spells as a witch, play tricks as a fairy, hunt as a werewolf or bite other sims as a vampire or zombie!
